						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying near the tank close to the village.</p>						

						<p>Circa 11th century.</p>						

						<p>It seems to record a gift of money. It mentions two persons named Maṁjarasa and Lōkarasa. The inscription is damaged.</p>						

